"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/453347","Ministry of Justice","false","2016-02-24","<p>We have not yet been informed of the date of the third Universal Periodic Review of the UK.</p>","Esher and Walton","Dominic Raab",,"2016-02-24T17:19:46.327Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/453347/answer","Biography information for Dominic Raab","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/453347/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/453347/answer",,,,,"54","Justice","Justice","2016-02-19","Human Rights","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Justice, what plans his Department has for consultation with (a) civil society groups, (b) the devolved administrations and (c) Northern Ireland to inform its report for the third cycle of the Human Rights Council Universal Periodic Review.","false","Biography information for Baroness Ritchie of Downpatrick","South Down","Ms Margaret Ritchie","27335"
