"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/453358","Ministry of Justice","false","2016-02-29","<p>The average length of time of cases in the Employment Tribunal can be located at <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/tribunals-statistics" target="_blank">https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/tribunals-statistics</a>.</p>","North West Cambridgeshire","Mr Shailesh Vara",,"2016-02-29T10:49:01.173Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/453358/answer","Biography information for Mr Shailesh Vara","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/453358/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/453358/answer",,,,,"54","Justice","Justice","2016-02-19","Employment Tribunals Service","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Justice, what the average length of time of cases in employment tribunals was in each of the last five years.","false","Biography information for Paul Blomfield","Sheffield Central","Paul Blomfield","27463"
