"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/453360","Northern Ireland Office","false","2016-02-24","<p>I recently held discussions on Bombardier with the Minister for Small Business, Industry and Enterprise and the Northern Ireland Minister for Enterprise, Trade and Investment. I will continue to discuss this issue with Government and Executive Ministers.</p>","Chipping Barnet","Mrs Theresa Villiers","27495 ; 27497","2016-02-24T15:50:43.593Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/453360/answer","Biography information for Theresa Villiers","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/453360/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/453360/answer",,,,,"21","Northern Ireland","Northern Ireland","2016-02-19","Bombardier: Redundancy","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Northern Ireland, what discussions she has had with the Secretary of State for Business, Innovation and Skills on job losses at Bombardier in Northern Ireland.","false","Biography information for Vernon Coaker","Gedling","Vernon Coaker","27496"
